00:00:58.650 --> 00:01:01.130
As a Peace Corps volunteer in West Africa

00:01:01.130 --> 00:01:03.255
he collaborated with UNICEF,

00:01:03.255 --> 00:01:05.737
the Safe Motherhood and
Child Survival Project,

00:01:05.737 --> 00:01:09.904
